description.excerpt: 基于python 3.7.6和pytorch 1.5.0对论文“Bag of Tricks for Image Classification with Convolutional Neural Networks”进行复现，验证了论文中的大部分技巧
The reproduction of paper "Bag of Tricks for Image Classification with Convolutional Neural Networks" (based on Pyorch)

invocation.excerpt: python3 train.py --ResNet_BCD True  --float16 True  --cosine_decay True  --batch_size 128  --smoothing_label True

python3 teacher.py  #:训练教师模型 
python3 teacher_label.py  #:产生教师标签 
python3 learn_from_teacher.py  #:训练学生模型
